---
import Main from "../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<Main>
    <header
        class="flex flex-col items-center px-4 py-20 md:py-36 text-center relative"
    >
        <h1
            class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-9xl font-bold font-teko text-yellow-400 uppercase tracking-widest transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105"
            style="text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #000000;"
        >
            Soviet Linux
        </h1>
        <p
            class="mt-2 text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-white font-bold font-maven max-w-xl leading-snug md:leading-relaxed"
        >
            <strong>The proletariat's distro</strong>
        </p>
        <p
            class="disclamer mt-2 text-sm sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 font-mono font-bold max-w-xl leading-snug border-t-2 border-red-600 pt-2"
            style="background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1); padding: 8px; border-radius: 5px;"
        >
            The heroic work continues to make <i>Soviet Linux</i> a daily tool of
            the worker's digital arsenal. Though it is not yet ready for daily use,
            <strong>all contributions are welcome!</strong>
        </p>

        <a
            href="https://discord.gg/5RVsSEej8M"
            class="mt-4 text-sm sm:text-lg text-yellow-400 font-bold uppercase border-2 border-yellow-400 px-3 py-2 hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-red-800 transition-colors duration-300"
        >
            Join the Discord Revolution!
        </a>
    </header>

    <div class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 ml-2 hidden md:block">
        <img
            src="/assets/penguin-sickle.svg"
            alt="Penguin Sickle"
            class="h-48 w-48 md:h-96 md:w-96"
        />
    </div>
    <div class="fixed bottom-0 right-0 mr-2 hidden md:block">
        <img
            src="/assets/penguin-hammer.svg"
            alt="Penguin Hammer"
            class="h-48 w-48 md:h-96 md:w-96"
        />
    </div>
</Main>
